<h2 id="my-results" class="headerLink">
    <a href="#my-results" class="header-mark"></a>My Results?</h2><figure><a class="lightgallery" href="/devlogs/backfire/2025-08-09-gmtk-25-results/images/results_screenshot.png" title="" data-thumbnail="/devlogs/backfire/2025-08-09-gmtk-25-results/images/results_screenshot.png" data-sub-html="<h2>Final Results for my submission</h2>"><img  loading="lazy" src=https://rustycruiselabs.github.io/devlogs/backfire/2025-08-09-gmtk-25-results/images/results_screenshot.png    height="674" width="1173"></a><figcaption class="image-caption">Final Results for my submission</figcaption>
